%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt85q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=d636eb8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWxRo2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWxRo2R.jpg&h=1a7a9910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28685e0ad1b91358de13887ca4f97310d11b6dcb","tid":1744910,"uid":134174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:29:02.000Z","msg":"唔好掉走然後扮唔知"},{"pid":"96bdc8847091d04f7774aeb28c9bd645d28b24a1","tid":1744910,"uid":154644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad58e89d2cf66925a7afc0685832ac2c95c9b49","tid":1744910,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:29:44.000Z","msg":"唔可以講唔俾人投票<br />\n因為犯法的"},{"pid":"73c29fe75268e9b751a026890c451e3639517f0c","tid":1744910,"uid":154644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:40:47.000Z","msg":"唔好唔比心投"}]}